<p>
<p>Of two events A and B, the following is given: P(A) = 0.60, P(B) = 0.40, P(A ∩ B) = 0.20 and P(A ∪ B) = 0.80. Are events A and B independent?</p>
</p>]]></text>
</questiontext>
<generalfeedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
</p>]]></text>
</generalfeedback>
<penalty>0</penalty>
<defaultgrade>1</defaultgrade>
<shuffleanswers>false</shuffleanswers>
<single>true</single>
<answernumbering>abc</answernumbering>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Yes, because P(A ∪ B)= P(A) + P(B) - P(A ∩ B)
</p>]]></text>
<feedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Yes, because P(A ∪ B)= P(A) + P(B) - P(A ∩ B): Incorrect
</p>]]></text>
</feedback>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Yes, because P(B | A) = P(B)
</p>]]></text>
<feedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Yes, because P(B | A) = P(B): Incorrect
</p>]]></text>
</feedback>
</answer>
<answer fraction="100" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
No, because P(A ∩ B) ≠ P(A) x P(B)
</p>]]></text>
<feedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
No, because P(A ∩ B) ≠ P(A) x P(B): Correct
</p>]]></text>
</feedback>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
No, because P(A ∪ B) ≠ P(A) + P(B)
</p>]]></text>
<feedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
No, because P(A ∪ B) ≠ P(A) + P(B): Incorrect
</p>]]></text>
</feedback>
</answer>
